   =20
      Pay to play
   =20
 =20
We talked a couple of times last week about situations in which you can pay=
 to play professional sports. The main ones I mentioned were Portuguese soc=
cer (one time), car racing (often) and bridge (pretty much all the time). A=
fterwards a bunch of readers emailed to mention polo, which honestly seems =
obvious in hindsight.
