om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">RIP Jim Simons</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">James Simons, arguably the greatest of=
 all hedge fund managers,=C2=A0died last week. <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35362511.256340/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLm=
NvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDUtMTAvamltLXNpbW9ucy1xdWFudC1raW5nLWF0LXJlb=
mFpc3NhbmNlLXRlY2hub2xvZ2llcy1kaWVzLWF0LTg2P2NtcGlkPUJCRDA1MTMyNF9NT05FWVNU=
