: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;">Every</a> <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/3536=
2511.256340/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyNC8wNS8xMC9idXNpbmVzcy9kZWF=
sYm9vay9qaW0tc2ltb25zLWRlYWQuaHRtbA/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd719babe" item=
prop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color=
