<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[1] One reader suggested *insider trading*? I =
think the answer there is obviously no but I guess it goes on the exam.</p>
</div>
<div id=3D"footnote-2" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[2] He also knew a lot about *recruiting* math=
ematicians, and had the important intuition that he should keep doing that =
when he left academia for finance, and not recruit finance people.</p>
</div>
<div id=3D"footnote-3" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[3] This is from pages 301 and 302 of <a href=
