olor: #ccc;">More Money Than God</a>, and yes, there is a discussion of the=
 risks of data mining that I have omitted (but that Renaissance obviously u=
nderstands).</p>
</div>
<div id=3D"footnote-4" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[4] Except that if the insider was giving him =
exhaustive financial updates, why wasn=E2=80=99t *he* charged? The SEC=E2=
=80=99s theory here is that Individual A was innocently talking to Poerio a=
nd expecting him not to trade, which works for =E2=80=9Cdoing very well=E2=
=80=9D but not for, like, 122 detailed due diligence sessions.</p>
</div>
